---
layout: layouts/error.njk
title: "Page Not Found"
description: "The page you are looking for does not exist or has been moved."
error_code: 404
permalink: /404.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
noindex: true
---
<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center lg:text-left prose">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">
      Ahhhhh!
      <span class="block text-2xl mt-2 text-stone-600">This page does not exist</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6">
      Don't get angry with us!<br/>
      We didn't hide your page on purpose...
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4">
      Head back to the <a href="/">homepage</a>.<br/>
      Or stay here and rock out with the Stones.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center lg:justify-start">
      <a href="/search/" class="btn btn--secondary">
        {% phosphor "magnifying-glass", "bold", { size: 20 } %}
        Find what you lost
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lg:col-span-2">
    {% youTube "_mEC54eTuGw", "The Rolling Stones - Angry" %}
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm prose text-center lg:col-span-3">
    Think this is a mistake?
    <a href="https://github.com/{{ build.issues.owner }}/{{ build.issues.repo }}/issues/new?labels=bug&title=404+Error+Report" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      Report an issue
    </a>
  </p>
</div>
